PRATT and WHITNEY
WASP AIRCRAFT ENGINE
THE PRATT & WHITNEY Model SICC-Wasp Aircraft motor
is a 14 cylinder twin row radial air-cooled engine. This model engine is
used in the twin motor Douglas DC-3 passenger plane. Power produced
by each engine is as follows:
